author: Cory Shaffer, cleveland.com
title: Cleveland men indicted in standoff outside strip club streamed encounter on Facebook Live
text: Dannel Hicks and Antonio Powell are charged with two dozen counts of attempted murder of a police officer in the Feb. 28 shootout with SWAT officers outside a Cleveland strip club.
